   28 00000000         ; Amount of memory (in bytes) allocated for Stack
   29 00000000         ; Tailor this value to your application needs
   30 00000000         ; <h> Stack Configuration
   31 00000000         ;   <o> Stack Size (in Bytes) <0x0-0xFFFFFFFF:8>
   32 00000000         ; </h>
   33 00000000         
   34 00000000         ; Main (MSP) stack — used during startup, in main() up
                        to
   35 00000000         ; vTaskStartScheduler(), and for all ISR frames afterwar
                       ds. The BLE
   36 00000000         ; stack's init (ns_ble_task_init etc.) recurses deeply, 
                       so we keep the
   37 00000000         ; original 2 KB here. Each FreeRTOS task has its own PSP
                        stack, see
   38 00000000         ; user/app_tasks.c.



